em>Abraham Kurian, VP of Information Technology WAIGlobal.</em></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal;\"> </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #444956; background-color: white; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">Join us at our “<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Master the Speed of Change”</span> event, where experts with decades of professional experience will reveal three practical strategies you can use to make speed a competitive weapon.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal;\"> </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #444956; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in; background-color: white; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">Event: Master the Speed of Change </span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #444956;\"><br /><strong><span style=\"border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in; background-color: white;\">Date: 2 August 2012</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in; background-color: white;\">Time: 16.00 – 19.00</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: #444956; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in; background-color: whi