(113, 231, '“Master the Speed of Change” seminar by PT BSI, Infor and Avnet IBM', 'master-the-speed-of-change-seminar-by-pt-bsi-infor-and-avnet-ibm', '', '<p>On November 21 , 2012 PT Bisnis Sistem Indonesia together with PT  Avnet Datamation Solutions (IBM) and Infor held a seminar with the title “Master the Speed of Change” atJW  Marriott Hotel, Jakarta.<br /><br />In the seminar, the audience learned about: <br /><br />·  Companies are embracing new technologies to improve financial consolidation, budgeting and planning processes, and reporting<br /><br />·   To focus on and establish the value that can be derived by capital expenditure in information technology, through value analysis and value engineering<br /><br />The audience learned about how ear how this relates to the solutions you are using and the exciting capabilities of the Infor Industry Suites, incorporating your Infor ERP solutions.<br /><br />Mr. Alexander Wibowo, Product Manager of PT Avnet Datamation Solutions shared the knowledge about smart collaboration to increased utilization.  Infor ERP LN combined with IBM\'s infrastructure offerings, optimize business performance and deliver rapid return on investment, low total cost of ownership and bottom-line business results</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"images/stories/BSIe20122.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\'Master the Speed of Change\' event\" width=\"550\" height=\"343\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"images/stories/BSIe20121.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\'Master the Speed of Change\' event\" width=\"552\" height=\"365\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"images/stories/BSIe20123.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\'Master the Speed of Change\' event\" width=\"553\" height=\"402\" /></p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 87, '2013-08-22 13:02:05', 849, '', '2021-03-03 08:29:24', 863, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2013-08-22 13:02:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fullt