(114, 233, 'Infor MyDay', 'infor-myday', '', '<h2>Infor MyDay for Manufacturing delivers role-specific, pre-defined and configurable metrics, reports, and alerts for key decision-making roles throughout a manufacturing enterprise.</h2>\r\n<p><strong>Do business better</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>Giving your employees authority to make the right decision is critical, but not enough to carry the day. You also need to give them tools to cut through extraneous business information so they can quickly focus on data specific to their roles and make the decision that’s best for your business.</p>\r\n<p>Whether you\'re a mixed-mode or project-based manufacturer, the odds are that if you have an enterprise resource planning (ERP) solution, you’re capturing every data point you need for effective decision-making. But often this information is trapped in an information silo or in documents and not easily accessed or analyzed. To empower employees with actionable business information in real-time, forward thinking manufacturers are looking to enhance their ERP solution in ways that minimize the time it takes employees to address major, day-to-day tasks.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Leverage experience.</strong><br /> Infor™ MyDay for Manufacturing delivers role-specific, predefined and configurable metrics, reports, and alerts for key decision-making roles throughout a manufacturing enterprise. The solution features roles across sales, operations, production, purchasing, finance, and human resources, each of which can be customized to meet the needs of manufacturers. Infor MyDay for Manufacturing gives executives and line of business employees better visibility into the critical data needed to complete daily tasks. In addition, Infor MyDay for Manufacturing delivers a single source of normalized data for improved reporting.</p>\r\n<p>By complementing your existing Infor solutions with Infor MyDay for Manufacturing, you can consolidate information from any data source into a holistic view of your business that supports better day-to-day decision-making.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Get business specific</strong>.<br /> Infor MyDay for Manufacturing helps leverage the powerful information captured and stored in Infor’s leading ERP solutions for manufacturers, including Infor ERP LN, Infor ERP SyteLine, Infor ERP VISUAL, and more. Featuring a dynamic web 2.0 user interface, the solution improves the speed and quality of decision-making at all levels of the enterprise. To facilitate fast and efficient communications of business information, the user interface is integrated into Infor ERP solutions through Infor Open SOA, Infor’s event-driven approach to service-oriented architecture.</p>\r\n<p>Employees using Infor MyDay can quickly identify which areas need immediate attention and, as a result, minimize the time to mitigate problems. With those opportunities identified, employees can use the Infor MyDay solution to easily and securely drill deep into the relevant business data stored in your enterprise solutions and retrieve information specific to a business problem or task. This makes it easier to investigate a business problem or challenge and reduce the time to correct that problem. In addition, Infor MyDay for Manufacturing can be combined with other Infor solutions, such as Infor PM and Infor Decisions, to expand your information analysis capabilities.</p>\r\n<p>With Infor MyDay for Manufacturing, your company gets a clear line of sight into your performance. The solution consolidates data from any source in your enterprise to provide multiple views of key manufacturing data that are tailored to individual employees and displayed on their computer screen. For example, a production planner can closely monitor and manage key performance indicators for his or her job, including planned vs. actual production, unplanned scrap by reason, resource utilization, and ontime completion.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Infor MyDay helps improve the efficiency and effectiveness of several major business processes including</strong>:</p>\r\n<p>Customer service. Infor MyDay makes it possible to learn the true cost of serving individual customers so you more effectively respond to mandates to reduce costs and add more customized services, such as adding radio frequency identification device (RFID) tags, shrink wrapping, or special labels. The solution delivers tools to help you analyze a wide range of specific business metrics, such as customer and product pricing, off-invoice discounts, and post-invoice discounts. With one view to the true cost of servicing individual customers and the ability to analyze order processing, accounts receivable, and inventory data, Infor MyDay helps you know what customers and products are the most profitable. With this insight, manufacturers can ensure their investments are being made in customers and products that produce the greatest return.</p>\r\n<p>Operational effectiveness. As with customer service, the true cost of producing a product can only be determined by analyzing a wide range of direct and indirect production costs. Infor MyDay provides tools for identifying trends like changes in commodity pricing, other costs, or quality issues. By identifying areas that can be immediately addressed, your company can continually eliminate unnecessary costs and improve quality. You can analyze material usage, resource usage, and other specific production-related metrics to get a true cost of quality. For example, the Infor MyDay solution can help a company spot situations where material and resource consumption are relatively high for the production level, which in all likelihood is an indication of a quality issue. As companies are increasingly forced to make tough decisions, the impact of a “one time” planner or scheduler’s decision is isolated, making it less likely manufacturers will take the wrong course of action.</p>\r\n<p>Cash flow. Infor MyDay lets you identify and analyze metrics that determine cash flow, which helps increase your ability to manage cash and minimize the consumption of working capital. The solution helps you quickly identify any changes in your cash flow position and drill into the details to find the cause, such as situations where customers are slow paying and where your perfect order rates are slipping. With this improved visibility, you have the ability to identify and act on problem areas, such as when customers are claiming unallowed discounts for unsalable products. With this critical information, companies can minimize the time to address cash-flow issues.</p>\r\n<p><strong>See results now</strong>.<br /> Faced with extraordinary financial pressures, manufacturers of all sizes are aggressively seeking ways to improve their decision making and operational efficiency. Infor MyDay for Manufacturing supports these strategic objectives by streamlining the processes individual employees use to access and analyze the relevant business information they need for making decisions that drive your overall success.</p>\r\n<p>Infor MyDay for Manufacturing helps you:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Reduce operational expenses</li>\r\n<li>Improve cash flow</li>\r\n<li>Boost profits</li>\r\n<li>Improve product quality</li>\r\n<li>Reduce time to correction for business problems</li>\r\n<li>Increase revenue</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>Give your employees the actionable business information they need to work more intelligently and efficiently with Infor MyDay for Manufacturing.</p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 91, '2013-08-22 13:18:02', 849, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2013-08-22 13:18:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 1, 0, 5, '', '', 1, 2426, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', '');
