(116, 235, 'Infor Decisions', 'infor-decisions', '', '<h2>Infor Decisions gives you greater insight into business performance so you can get ahead of business conditions rather that letting those conditions get ahead of you.</h2>\r\n<p><strong>Do business better</strong>.<br /> Strategy and tactics operate in a complex relationship that experts have debated for centuries. Tactics without strategy amount to shooting in the dark, but strategy is only as good as its tactics. Both are essential, but each requires a different thinking process</p>\r\n<p>By pairing Infor™ MyDay and Infor Decisions, you get a matched set of solutions that elevate your strategy and sharpen your tactics. Infor MyDay improves daily tactical execution by guiding key personnel in completing their daily tasks. Infor Decisions helps you formulate more effective strategies to maximize the long-term value of your tactics.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Leverage experience</strong>.<br /> Infor Decisions is the newest additional to our assortment of Evolve components, which leverage the power of Infor Open SOA to help you preserve the value of the applications you already have, add features that you want when you want them, and connect to Infor\'s next-generation solutions with an expanding range of new functionality. You\'ll also reduce risk by eliminating the disruptive cycle of costly rip and replace upgrades. Our solutions embody decades of experience in manufacturing, finance, retail, asset management, supply chain management, and everything else you need to make your business agile and successful.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Get business specific</strong>.<br /> Infor Decisions connects analysis, planning, and action together in the most efficient combination, so that you can make better decisions and act on those decisions more rapidly. You\'ll also have more confidence in your decisions because you\'ll know why your choice was sound. With a solution that rapidly lets you analyze business performance, and measure changes in performance, you\'ll get ahead of business conditions rather that letting those conditions get ahead of you.</p>\r\n<p>The product of thousands of hours of research, Infor Decisions arises from our experts\' detailed understanding of a range of industries and the individual requirements that each industry demands. Our in-depth interviews and detailed research add a degree of built-in expertise that an army of consultants would charge millions of dollars to share. We\'ve collected all the best practices of the companies in your industry and hard-wired those practices into Infor Decisions so that you don\'t have to go on reinventing the wheel or guessing what to do next. When you reduce doubt, you reduce risk, too. While decision-support tools are not new to industry, Infor Decisions takes the concept to a new level by connecting directly to the systems that drive your business, both for analysis and for action.</p>\r\n<p>The Result is a library of roles and analyses that we\'ve defined to encompass and support the critical responsibilities in a wide range of industries, including financial professionals, production planners, and operations managers. Infor Decisions will make your company more effective from day one and help you raise performance to a new level.</p>\r\n<p><strong>See results now</strong>.<br /> Infor Decisions is an integral part of a growing list of Infor solutions we\'ll be releasing over the next few years. You\'ll be able to incorporate this advanced solution through a rapid, non-disruptive rollout that takes advantage of Infor Open SOA for top performance and maximum flexibility. You\'ll gain better insight and analysis for more confident decisions.</p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 91, '2013-08-22 13:20:23', 849, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2013-08-22 13:20:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 1, 0, 3, '', '', 1, 2581, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', ''),
