>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 22.22222328186035px; color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">Increase on-time launches to 98%.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 22.22222328186035px; color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 22.22222328186035px; color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">Infor PLM solutions help you with:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 22.22222328186035px; color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Integrated regulatory compliance</strong>—Protect your brand integrity and ensure compliance with appropriate standards and regulations.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 22.22222328186035px; color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Collaboration</strong>—Use social networking tools to get your customers, suppliers, and partners on the same page and improve efficiency and productivity.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong style=\"font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 22.22222328186035px; color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Product lifecycle intelligence</strong><span style=\"font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 22.22222328186035px; color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">—Leverage data across your enterprise in real time to make better decisions about your products.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong style=\"font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 22.22222328186035px; color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Project, portfolio, and bid management</strong><span style=\"font-size: 14.444444