(118, 237, 'Infor Supply Chain Management (SCM)', 'infor-supply-chain-management-scm', '', '<p style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: middle; background-color: #f5f5f5; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; vertical-align: middle; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.22222328186035px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">The power of Infor SCM</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; line-height: 18.765625px; color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\">Infor Supply Chain Management combines best in class solutions with industry-specific functionality, giving you the power to plan and execute your supply chain strategies faster and more profitably, from strategic and tactical planning to execution. With analytics at the core, you\'ll get the tools you need to optimize your end-to-end supply chain and harness the power of social networking to collaborate more effectively internally, as well as  with customers, partners, and suppliers. Gain greater visibility into your supply chain to optimize utilization of resources and labor, improve inventory and shipping accuracy, deliver the perfect order every time, and respond faster to customer opportunities and market fluctuations.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #143b71; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 22.22222328186035px;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #143b71; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 22.22222328186035px;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: middle; background-color: #f5f5f5; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; vertical-align: middle; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.22222328186035px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">Specialized by industry</strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px; text-align: justify;\">Infor SCM offers industry-specific functionality for a range of industries, including:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 22.22222328186035px;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: middle; background-color: #f5f5f5; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 60px; color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; vertical-align: middle; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.22222328186035px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">Food &amp; beverage</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; line-height: 18.765625px; color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\">Optimize the supply chain, from forecasting to production to customer delivery to boost profits. Account for volume-based constraints,  such as tanks, ovens, and freezers, to maximize throughput, improving productivity and  reducing waste.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.