s and PARs.  Control your supply chain costs and optimize the use of your production capacity. Effectively plan co- and by-products, and determine the least-cost formulation.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: middle; background-color: #f5f5f5; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 60px; color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; vertical-align: middle; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.22222328186035px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">Distribution</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\">Improve collaboration with customers and suppliers, and better manage supply chain complexity to drive higher service levels, lower inventory, and lower supply chain costs.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: middle; background-color: #f5f5f5; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 60px; color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"line-height: 22.21875px;\">Logistics providers</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\">Make faster and better deci