hronized ones with Infor\'s comprehensive business intelligence tools and </span></span><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\">innovative integration capabilities. Right from your mobile device, you’ll have access to robust reporting capabilities, analytics pre-built to meet specific industry needs, personalized dashboards, workflows and alerts—with changes synced automatically to your desktop. The result? Your business software is no longer a one-way street.</span><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 18.76736068725586px;\">.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 18.76736068725586px; color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 18.76736068725586px; color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; vertical-align: middle; background-color: #f5f5f5; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 22.22222328186035px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 22.22222328186035px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: middle; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Get software that talks back</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 18.76736068725586px; text-align: justify;\">With Infor™ Analytics, you get software that talks back, monitoring critical processes that you identify and letting you know of potential problems anytime, anywhere. You can drill down into issues, analyze them on the spot, and get the information you need to keep things from getting out of control. You’ll be able to:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 18.76736068725586px; text-align: justify;\"> </span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 18.76736068725586px; text-align: justify;\">Transform information into actionable insights.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\">Monitor and drive your business anytime, from anywhere.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\">Unlock the potential of data in previously siloed enterprise applications.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\">Speed decision making with personalized dashboards and role-based analytics.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\">Proactively address problems through workflows and alerts</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; vertical-align: middle; background-color: #f5f5f5; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 22.22222328186035px; text-align: justify;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 22.22222328186035px;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: middle; background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Improve decision making with information at your fingertips</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 18.76736068725586px; text-align: justify;\">Infor Analytics gives you a comprehensive business intelligence platform that can be used in any domain or industry. Powered by an in-memory database,the solution offers a unique, multi-purpose web front-end, as well as mobile capabilities that put information at your fingertips. Easily integrated with both Infor and non-Infor data sources, Infor Analytics lets you take advantage of information that resides in previously disconnected systems and get a real-time view of your entire business operation. You get all the tools you need to analyze, manage, and drive your business in one complete package. These include:</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 18.76736068725586px; text-align: justify;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 18.76736068725586px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"images/kotak-hitam-2.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 10px;\" /> User-friendly reporting tools and pre-built reports that are ready to use right out of the box, so you can put the power of analytics directly into the hands of power users, without help from IT.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 18.76736068725586px; text-align: justify;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 18.76736068725586px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"images/kotak-hitam-2.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 10px;\" /> “What-if” scenarios and driver-based planning to improve both the quality of decisions and your confidence in them.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 18.76736068725586px; text-align: justify;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 18.76736068725586px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"images/kotak-hitam-2.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 10px;\" /> Automatic synchronization of information through the innovative Infor ION Business Vault, which monitors, organizes, and stores your business data.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 60px;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\">Infor Analytics gives you a comprehensive business intelligence platform that can be used in any domain or industry. Powered by an in-memory database,the solution offers a unique, multi-purpose web front-end, as well as mobile capabilities that put information at your fingertips. Easily integrated with both Infor and non-Infor data sources, Infor Analytics lets you take advantage of information that resides in previously disconnected systems and get a real-time view of your entire business operation. You get all the tools you need to analyze, manage, and drive your business in one complete package. These include:</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\"><strong>Finance —</strong> Keep track of actuals and budgets for revenue and costs, profit and loss, balance sheet, and cash flow statements, as well as cost center information.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.3em;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\"><strong>Sales —</strong> Track sales orders, bookings, revenues, and gross profits, and analyze both sales performance and profitability by product and customer.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\"><strong>Operations —</strong> Monitor critical factors like production orders, in time production, and quality.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\">Based on decades of industry experience, Infor Analytic’s industry-driven analytics include capabilities for:</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\"><strong>Healthcare —</strong> Identify cost savings opportunities, improve hiring and personnel management, and increase collaboration with analytics built by healthcare experts specifically for the healthcare industry.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\"><strong>Hospitality —</strong> Get a real-time view of your business, analyze key metrics such as occupancy rates and profitability by outlet, and increase profitability with analytics built to meet the unique needs of the multi-faceted hospitality industry.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.3em;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\"><strong>Manufacturing —</strong> Get a big picture view of key metrics such as total business inventory and manufacturing throughput, detect drivers for quality issues, and more, with pre-packaged, easily integrated reports and dashboards based on decades of experience.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px; color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px; color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Transform information into actionable insight</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px; color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">With Infor Analytics, you’ll get a real-time view across your organization and unlock the power of previously siloed data sources. You can let your systems do the work for a change, delivering information about exceptions and potential issues automatically — wherever you are. You’ll make better decisions more quickly, be more responsive, and solve problems proactively, rather than reactively.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #525253; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.765625px;\"> </span></p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 9, '2014-01-02 10:36:34', 849, '', '2021-03-03 08:16:02', 863, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-01-02 10:36:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 31, 0, 2, '', '', 1, 9616, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', ''),
