(195, 320, 'Apa yang dapat dilakukan oleh ERP System?', 'apa-yang-dapat-dilakukan-oleh-erp-system', '', '<p><img src=\"images/banners/Apa%20yang%20dapat%20dilakukan%20ERP%20System.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"solusi erp\" title=\"erp\" /></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Karakteristik yang paling menonjol di dalam sistem ERP adalah sistem tersebut dibentuk di atas satu basis data yang komprehensif untuk berbagi data atau informasi di seluruh departemen perusahaan. Tujuan utama sistem ERP adalah untuk mengotomatiskan proses bisnis agar membuat bisnis lebih efisien dan memberikan visibilitas yang lebih baik ke dalam proses tersebut.</p>\r\n<p><br /> Tetapi untuk mendapatkan manfaat dari sistem ERP sendiri, bisnis perlu mengintegrasikan sistem ERP mereka dengan sistem perusahaan yang dimilikinya. Ini seringkali sulit; karena tantangan integrasi sistem ERP sendiri melibatkan beberapa faktor di antaranya yaitu usia sistem, komponen atau struktur sistem, dan kebutuhan untuk mengintegrasikan aplikasi dan sistem baru ke dalam sistem ERP..</p>\r\n<p><br /> Sistem ERP dirancang untuk mengintegrasikan dan mengotomatisasi fungsi-fungsi pemrosesan bisnis back-office. Sistem ERP dimaksudkan untuk membuat hidup lebih mudah dan memungkinkan peningkatan produktivitas bisnis perusahaan. Lebih jauh lagi, sistem ERP dapat membuat arsitektur bisnis jauh lebih kuat, namun pendekatan yang salah dapat menimbulkan konsekuensi yang sebaliknya.</p>\r\n<p><br /> Integrasi adalah unsur yang sangat penting dalam sistem ERP. Integrasi antara proses bisnis akan membantu pengembangan komunikasi dan distribusi informasi, yang mengarah ke peningkatan produktivitas, kecepatan, dan kinerja yang luar biasa . Tujuan utama sistem ERP adalah mengintegrasikan informasi dan proses dari semua divisi dalam suatu perusahaan, sehingga mendapatkan kemudahan akses dan alur kerja yang terstruktur.</p>\r\n<p><br /> Integrasi ini biasanya dilakukan dengan membangun sebuah repositori database tunggal yang berkomunikasi dengan beberapa aplikasi software, yang dapat digunakan oleh berbagai divisi dari sebuah perusahaan. Repositori database tunggal biasanya berisi berbagai statistik bisnis dan informasi tertentu yang dibutuhkan oleh masing-masing divisi.</p>\r\n<p><br /> Meskipun konfigurasi yang sempurna adalah membangun sebuah sistem ERP tunggal untuk seluruh organisasi, namun banyak organisasi yang lebih besar biasanya menggunakan sistem fungsional tunggal untuk masing-masing divisi dan kemudian baru perlahan-lahan diintergrasikan dengan divisi lainnya. Tipe pembangunan sistem fungsional tunggal seperti ini bisa benar-benar memakan waktu dan biaya yang sangat mahal.</p>\r\n<p><br /> Sistem ERP terdiri dari beberapa modul untuk menciptakan aliran informasi yang sesuai dengan kebutuhan di level departemen dan level perusahaan. Ini dapat dibeli secara fungsional modul atau per paket yang disesuaikan berdasarkan kebutuhan organisasi. Beberapa modul software ERP yang dapat diintegrasikan ke dalam satu sistem ERP biasanya adalah:</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Accounting and Financial Management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Human Resource &amp; Payroll Management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Inventory Management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Customer Relationship Management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><br /> Penggunaan sistem ERP akan dapat mengurangi biaya, mengoptimalkan proses bisnis, dan memastikan managemen berjalan dengan baik. Inti dari software ERP membawa setiap aspek bisnis yang Anda jalankan berada di satu atap untuk menghasilkan bisnis yang berkesinambungan terus menerus. Dengan ERP, Anda bahkan dapat mengoptimalkan rantai pasokan produksi di perusahaan Anda.</p>\r\n<p><br /> Kemudahan dengan ERP tersebut dapat menjadi pertimbangan Anda untuk memilih sistem ERP yang sesuai dengan kebutuhan bisnis Anda. Ingin tahu lebih banyak mengenai sistem ERP Indonesia silakan hubungi ke +6221 304 90008 atau email ke ptbsi@ptbsi.co.id.</p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 86, '2018-07-30 07:22:12', 855, '', '2021-03-02 04:26:49', 863, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2018-07-30 07:22:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 3, 0, 26, 'erp system, erp sistem, sistem erp, Software erp indonesia, software eam indonesia, sistem erp indonesia, mudah dengan erp, mudahdenganerp', 'Tujuan utama sistem ERP adalah untuk mengotomatiskan proses bisnis agar membuat bisnis lebih efisien dan memberikan visibilitas yang lebih baik ke dalam proses tersebut.', 1, 3989, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', ''),
(197, 322, 'Ini sifat kepribadian kamu berdasarkan 12 Shio di Tahun Babi 2019', 'sifat-kepribadian-berdasarkan-12-shio-di-tahun-babi-2019', '', '<p><span style=\"color: #555555; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Kamu mungkin tahu ada 12 hewan zodiak Tiongkok (Shio) yang digunakan untuk mewakili tahun Babi di tahun 2019. Lebih dari 2.000 tahun yang lalu Sistem 12 shio telah ada dalam budaya Cina sejak dinasti Qin. Seiring berjalannya waktu, shio menjadi semakin terintegrasi ke dalam kehidupan sehari-hari, dengan makna dan karakteristik berbeda yang diberikan pada masing-masing hewan. Shio dapat digunakan untuk menentukan keberuntungan Anda seperti kesesuaian pernikahan, kecocokan karier, waktu terbaik untuk memiliki bayi, dan banyak lagi. Dalam infografis dibawah ini, cari tahu apa shio dari tahun kelahiran mu dan cek kepribadian mu berdasarkan shio tersebut.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"images/INFOGRAFIK-SHIO-BABI-2019-PT-BSI.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"INFOGRAFIK-SHIO-BABI-2019-PT-BSI\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"> </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">1. TIKUS</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Tikus itu pintar, pemikir cepat; sukses, tetapi puas dengan menjalani kehidupan yang tenang dan damai. Optimis dan energik, orang yang lahir pada tahun Tikus disukai oleh semua.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">2. KERBAU</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Kerbau adalah pekerja keras di latar belakang, cerdas dan dapat diandalkan, tetapi tidak pernah menuntut pujian. Lembu itu jujur dan sungguh-sungguh. Jarang kehilangan kesabaran, mereka berpikir secara logis dan menjadi pemimpin yang hebat.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">3. HARIMAU</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Harimau adalah orang yang berani dan aktif yang menyukai tantangan dan petualangan yang baik dalam hidup. Mereka baik dan murah hati. Hewan, musik, atau hal-hal lain yang membutuhkan imajinasi baik untuk mereka.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">4. KELINCI</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Kelinci sungguh-sungguh dengan segala yang mereka lakukan; mereka hanya meminta orang lain memperlakukan mereka dengan cara yang sama. Mereka terus bergerak menuju tujuan mereka, tidak peduli negatif apa pun yang diberikan orang lain kepada mereka.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">5. NAGA</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Naga adalah sosok yang kuat dan mandiri, tetapi mereka mendambakan dukungan dan cinta. Naga sangat pandai dalam merencanakan dan menghasilkan ide. Tetapi mereka membutuhkan orang lain untuk membantu dengan detail lain-lain.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">6. ULAR</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Ular memiliki pikiran yang dalam dan kompleks, tetapi jika mereka mencintai, mereka mencintai dengan sepenuh hati. Ular itu lucu dan canggih. Dalam lingkungan yang kacau, mereka adalah mata badai. Ular mampu bertahan dan dengan tenang memikirkan solusi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">7. KUDA</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Kuda penuh energi, rajin belajar dan atletis, mereka sangat percaya mengejar mimpi. Alih-alih kekayaan dan ketenaran, kebahagiaan adalah yang memotivasi mereka.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">8. KAMBING</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Kambing penuh kasih dan tidak mementingkan diri sendiri, selalu berpikir untuk orang lain, bahkan jika itu bertentangan dengan minat mereka sendiri.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">9. MONKEY</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Monyet adalah orang iseng ringan yang memiliki kemampuan untuk mencapai semua impian mereka. Mereka bersedia mendengarkan kritik dan belajar dari kesalahan mereka. Mereka adalah pemikir yang tenang dan logis.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">10. ROOSTER</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Ayam jantan serius dalam pekerjaan mereka. Mereka lugas dan tegas dalam tindakan mereka. Mereka akan langsung mengkritik apa yang mereka lihat tidak layak dan perfeksionis. Mereka logis dan pandai mengelola tim.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">11. DOG</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Anjing adalah sahabat sejati dan mitra paling andal. Mereka tidak akan pernah meninggalkan teman, keluarga, atau pekerjaan mereka. Mereka juga pandai membantu orang lain menemukan dan memperbaiki kebiasaan buruk mereka.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">12. BABI</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">Babi memiliki kepribadian yang indah dan diberkati dengan keberuntungan dalam hidup. Babi mungkin tidak menonjol di tengah orang banyak. Tetapi mereka sangat realistis.</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 86, '2019-01-29 03:48:36', 855, '', '2021-03-02 04:24:53', 863, 863, '2021-03-03 06:45:13', '2019-01-29 03:48:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 11, 0, 24, 'sifat kepribadian bedasarkan shio, shio tahun babi, shio 2019, shio babi 2019, keburuntungan shio, shio karier.', '12 Shio Tahun Babi yang dapat digunakan untuk menentukan keberuntungan Anda seperti kesesuaian pernikahan, kecocokan karier, waktu terbaik untuk memiliki bayi. ', 1, 10875, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', ''),
(198, 323, 'Adapting to Changing Consumer Demands with a Flexible Supply Chain in Manufacturing Industry', 'supply-chain-manufacturing-industry', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"images/banners/Banner%20Blog%20%2021.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"flexible supply chain in Manufacturing Industry\" title=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Every year automotive companies release new cars that are more advanced in terms of design, machinery, and technology. Each one is better than the last. As time evolves, vehicles become more and more sleek and aerodynamic, varied, and technologically improved. Years ago, car types and models are not as varied as today. Technological features inside the car are also not as much as today. Automotive companies have to acquire flexibility in order to achieve the advancements.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The needs of customers change every time, so therefore to fulfill the needs of the customer, the automotive industry has to have the ability to adapt to the changing needs of the customer. If companies are unable to cope with the customer’s demands and are inflexible sooner or later the company is going to experience stagnancy or regression, even bankruptcy. However, following the customer’s demands come with their own set of challenges as the demands affect how the vehicle is going to be produced.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The automotive company may experience difficulties when they try to adapt to fulfill the changing needs of customers. One of them is the complex designing process to the manufacturing process of the vehicle. How to translate the design properly into a prototype and enable the prototype to be mass-produced. The way engineers fit the spare parts and machines of the vehicle into the body of the car no matter how small or how complicated. If along the way the design has to be restarted after trials and errors, will that cause the release date to be pushed back? With the release date being pushed back, it will surely generate money loss which is what most companies avoid</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">What if there is a software that could relieve the pains stated above while streamlining the workflow and control it at the same time? ERP enables a company to synchronize systems inside the company and streamlining processes in the company. The implementing ERP in the company will result in an increase in efficiency and productivity because all information is shared and work progress would be tracked easily. Furthermore, the software is accessible just with the touch of the fingertips. The contribution of manufacturing flexibility to overall company performance will increase.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Infor LN is an ERP software provided by PT BSI that guarantees simplified workflow and synchronization of data. Infor LN controls the process of designing to the process of flexible manufacturing in a single line with synchronized data, making it simple to coordinate and be organized.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Infor LN made it possible for a program to be completely managed. Complete program management to take care of the new product launch is crucial. Infor LN has advantages such as collaborative environment, product data accessibility, program management, and project management. Collaborative environment enables the synchronization of engineering, acquisition, manufacturing, and customer across all stages of the product development process in a dynamic manner, making it possible to achieve flexibility in manufacturing. Product data accessibility makes the singular source to access product drawings and information in the proper context and format needed for supply chain development possible and safeguards the important project assets. Program management creates a configurable workflow in order to support the product development process and supporting full-market launch through providing project status, and transparent risk and cost for the product launch. Program management generates integrated project management for managing and tracks programs and sub-projects starting from tasks and activities to costs in detail.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">With Infor LN, it is possible to plan for supplier release when the demand is high or takes a long time to ship and trace and track the quality of the products. Infor LN has an advantage in terms of supply chain efficiency in ordering, through EDI, along with full visibility, in order to know exactly the suppliers\' ability to fulfill and the impact on the schedules of deadlines. Collaboration along with co-mingling with the ability to handle complex sourcing arrangements which means keeping control and efficiencies high is also possible with Infor LN. Infor LN also has the ability to react to the supply chain disruptions, re-source when needed and understand the effects to the customers, production and the financials.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">For more information about the solution please contact our phone at +6221 304 90008 or <a href=\"https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=628111221789&amp;text=Hallo%20PT%20Realta...\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Whatsapp\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WhatsApp +628111221789</a> (Chat Only) or our email at ptbsi@ptbsi.co.id<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 86, '2019-10-16 03:14:00', 862, '', '2021-03-03 04:50:00', 863, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2020-04-23 10:39:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 7, 0, 22, 'supply chain, erp in automotive industry, erp, erp system, software erp terbaik, erp, erp system, software erp terbaik, eam, software eam, EAM Software indonesia terbaik, enterprise asset management system, erp infor ln, infor LN, infor system, infor erp', 'Along with the change of times, companies have to be flexible in order to adapt to the customers changing needs.', 1, 747, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', ''),
(203, 328, 'The Importance of Valid Information Exchange in the Automotive Industry', 'valid-information-exchange-in-the-automotive-industry', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"images/banners/Banner%20Blog.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"the importance of valid information exchange in the Automotive Industry\" title=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In the automotive industry, all sorts of information should be communicated. Despite the sales team and production managers know the number of vehicles being produced, the inventory team should also be informed about production quantity as well. When this is done, they could optimize the stocks in the warehouse, and not have to order over stock spare parts.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The importance of the access of information in the automotive industry boils down to achieving a speedy and smooth production process. Because with a smooth and speedy production process, no project would be delayed and cost reduction on production. It is what manufacturing companies strive to achieve.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In order to achieve a smooth and speedy production process, information must be from single source and integrated data. The information must be in sync with the receivers of the information. If the information has more than one source it could potentially be misleading. Because every department needs to have one data as a reference that is used together. That data should be applicable in every single step of the production process. As an example, each department should be informed about the number of vehicles the company wants to produce. Because the information impacts the decision of the inventory team in terms of optimizing stocks available. The information will also impact the engineering team as they have to calculate for the machine capacity to be able to produce the quantity that has been set.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If there are miscommunications, it may lead to a production process that will not be smooth. Thus it will cause the project to be delayed and the operation cost will spike. This scenario is what people in the manufacturing industries avoid. Delaying a project because of a troublesome production process is a costly mistake that companies in the manufacturing industries do not want to experience.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The access to information is also important for external parties as well. Most notably suppliers. Suppliers need to be informed about the amount that the automotive company wants to produce and when the order should be delivered, so they can prepare to produce the quantity and timeline schedule that the company needs. This is so that the operators have easy, restriction-free, and standardized access to information</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">This could also be seen after production when the products reach the customers, access to the data is still important to maintain spare parts stock for service purposes or when there are factory defects it will be easily replaced or recalled. Furthermore, the after-sales data exchange could also be used to be analyzed for be a reference for future product development.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">That is how important access of information is in the manufacturing industry. With a proper exchange of information, it ensures that the production process will run smoothly and efficiently.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Because access of information is crucial in making sure that all production process runs smoothly. It is essential that automotive companies implement an ERP system for their company.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">ERP system is a system that will simplify the access to information. All information and data are compiled into one system, enabling easy and clear access to information. The information is also from one source making it reliable and integrated. ERP implementation also enables increased safety and security. PT Bisnis Sistem Indonesia (BSI), a leading ERP system provider in Indonesia has been successfully assisting clients to align their company process with Infor LN since 1998.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">For more information about the solution please contact our phone at +6221 304 90008 or <a href=\"https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=628111221789&amp;text=Hallo%20PT%20Realta...\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Whatsapp\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WhatsApp +628111221789</a> (Chat Only) or our email at ptbsi@ptbsi.co.id<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 86, '2020-04-22 06:27:37', 862, '', '2021-03-03 04:40:50', 863, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2020-04-22 06:27:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 9, 0, 21, 'automotive industry, information system, erp, erp system, software erp terbaik, erp infor ln, infor LN, infor system, infor erp', 'the importance of the [sl1] access of information in the automotive industry and the impacts of proper communication.', 1, 570, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', ''),
(204, 329, 'Transactions and Activities that could be Automated in the Automotive Industry', 'automated-transactions-activites-automotive-industry', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"images/banners/Banner%20Blog%20%200.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"transactions and activities that can be automated | ERP Infor\" title=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Progressing along with time, from industry 1.0 to 4.0. Factories become more advanced. From the previously relying on the strength of animals or humans to coals and now electricity and renewable resources. Now everything is controlled by machines that will follow our commands just with the push of a button. Everything has turned out to be faster and more efficient, in comparison to the previous industrial movement.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Automotive factories also experience technological advancements without exception. From being cast and built by humans completely, to completely built by robots. Previously having very limited quantities, now mass-produced everywhere. Times change, customer’s wants and needs also change. Surely, the automotive factory wants to be faster and more efficient.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Key is Automization!</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Automotive factories have to keep up with the demands of the customer. Factories that produce automotive vehicles must have the capacity to produce vehicles customer wants to buy, mass-producing the vehicles at a low cost and be efficient in using resources and time. To achieve that, the key is the automation of each transactions, process &amp; activity.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">After reaching the goals above, the factory has to be integrated between divisions, is capable of planning the release of the vehicle from start to finish, and has a controlled workflow to ensure from point A to B is executed properly and within the deadline. Therefore, the production costs will be much cheaper and efficient in resource and time.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Is there a system that could help?</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">ERP system can help automotive factories achieve this. Because the ERP system has the capability of integrating between divisions in the factory, plan the vehicle release from start to finish, and streamlining the workflow into one line, controlling it and making sure that nothing gets off track. Integration between departments are important as it minimizes miss-communication that could potentially result in fatal mistakes.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you are not informed about what is ERP, ERP is a software and system that is used by companies to manage their daily business activities, such as finance, procurement, project, HR, etc. This system could facilitate business with real-time and accurate information, making it easy to make a proper business decision based on the generated data. Through gathering the transaction data together from various sources, the ERP system avoids data duplication by giving data integrity.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">ERP system is capable of automatically sourcing spare parts that a certain vehicle needs. The system contacts suppliers of a certain spare part immediately after a vehicle is set for production. The system also immediately places an order and pays after that. Then, the components will be ready and lining up together with other components to be built into the car just in time.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The ERP system can automate the collection of data between divisions. When each division input data into the system, the system immediately compiles the data and makes the changes visible in real-time. This is exceptionally helpful for the finance team as it becomes simpler to audit purchases, cash flow, and sales using the data contained in the system, and calculates the balance based on the data of purchases, sales, and cash flow.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The production in the factory could be controlled automatically by the system. The process could be started just with the touch of a button and monitored through the system. Enabling people to monitor the factory situation, despite being far away from the factory.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The advantages stated above such as automatically sourcing spare parts, automatic data collection and automatic production process control are all possible through ERP. Because the advancements are possible, it is certain that the processes in the company will be faster and more efficient. With more speed and efficiency, everything will be done faster, the factory can produce more within the time planned, and the finance team can audit finances faster.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In Indonesia, PT Bisnis Sistem Indonesia (BSI) provides an ERP system called Infor LN. PT BSI has been established since 1998 and has been helping clients to align their business process to Infor LN successfully since then.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">For more information about the solution please contact our phone at +6221 304 90008 or <a href=\"https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=628111221789&amp;text=Hallo%20PT%20Realta...\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Whatsapp\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WhatsApp +628111221789</a> (Chat Only) or our email at ptbsi@ptbsi.co.id<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 86, '2020-04-22 06:37:04', 862, '', '2021-03-03 04:32:05', 863, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2020-04-23 02:38:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 8, 0, 19, 'Automate, Automated Process, Automated Transaction, Factory, erp, erp system, software erp terbaik', 'Automatable activities in the automotive industry that will make the processes quicker and more efficient.', 1, 572, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', ''),
(199, 324, 'Indonesia’s Automotive Industry 4.0 Symposium', 'indonesia-automotive-symposium', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"images/banners/Indonesias%20Automotive%20Industry%204.0%20Symposium%20Header.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Indonesia’s Automotive Industry 4.0 Symposium Header\" title=\"Indonesia’s Automotive Industry 4.0 Symposium Header\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">On the 20th of November 2019, the event Indonesia’s Automotive Industry 4.0 Symposium is held and attended by more than 80 people who have expertise in the field of automotive manufacturing assembled. The event begins with a keynote speech by Mr. Heru Gunawan, SE, M.T as the Head of Sub Directorate for Maritime Industry Development Program, Transportation Equipment, and Defense Equipment from the Ministry of Industry.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"images/banners/Indonesias%20Automotive%20Industry%204.0%20Symposium.JPG\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Indonesia’s Automotive Industry 4.0 Symposium\" title=\"Indonesia’s Automotive Industry 4.0 Symposium\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The keynote speech discusses Indonesia’s automotive road map and hopes, aspirations &amp; goals towards industry 4.0 in the 2030 Indonesia automotive system. Indonesia aspires to be an automotive industry leader in ASEAN. This means they have to produce on a large scale. In order to manufacture automotive spare parts on a large scale smoothly, a system such as Infor LN is needed. Because Infor LN ensures a smooth production line no matter the amounts of products to be produced.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"images/banners/Indonesias%20Automotive%20Industry%204.0%20Symposium%20Kemenperin.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Indonesia’s Automotive Industry 4.0 Symposium\" title=\"Indonesia’s Automotive Industry 4.0 Symposium Infor\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Afterward, the event is followed by a panel discussion. The panelists are Mr. Heru Gunawan, Mr. Matthew Adley as Infor’s Industry &amp; Solution Strategist, Ir. Hadi Surjadipraja as Secretary-General of GIAMM, Mr. Sommy Lumadjeng as the Chairman of Askarindo, and Mrs. Lystiani Ria Dewi as the Prsident Director of PT. FSCM Manufacturing Indonesia. With the moderator: Mr. I Gusti Putu Suryawirawan as the Head Commisionary of PT. Krakatau Steel (BUMN) and Special Assistant for the Minister of Economy Coordinator. Each panelist shared their insight about their experiences about their perspective in the automotive industry and how Infor will help or has helped them. <br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">ERP technology is discussed next. The speaker is Matthew Adley. This era is the age of automotive industry transformation; so therefore, the automotive trends of 2021 are to prepare for industry 4.0. The transition between the old ERP system &amp; the new ERP system is also discussed. Infor also is capable of integrating information from the frontline of production and the end line of production making it efficient and simple.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The event was continued with the customer sessions. The theme Enabling Digital with CloudSuite is presented by Matthew Adley. The theme discusses when companies digitalize their traditional manufacturing processes, companies are able to optimize their supply chain, reducing development cycles, increasing efficiencies and driving down costs. The cloud system has advantages of secure, stable and available solutions regarding security and risks. The cloud system is also capable of being up to date with the latest innovations in analytics, social collaboration, extensibility, and AI in relation to the adoption of innovation. Another advantage of the cloud system is that it enables access of data anywhere, anytime regardless of device &amp; browser. The cloud system could also scale and predict costs as the business grows.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"images/banners/Indonesias%20Automotive%20Industry%204.0%20Symposium%20Infor.JPG\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Indonesia’s Automotive Industry 4.0 Symposium\" title=\"Indonesia’s Automotive Industry 4.0 Symposium Infor\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Next, Mrs. Lee Luan Aw as the principal solution consultant for Infor presents about modernization with Infor LN CloudSuite. Modernization is important as business models are changing. Their focus is no longer about pushing a product to be released but putting out products that are catered towards customers. Infor also modernizes themselves by continuously improving to serve customers better. The newest addition of Infor’s improvement is Infor CloudSuite. So now businesses are not tied to an on-premise system if they wish to use Infor for their manufacturing line. New features of the system are also discussed, which are improved with the new interface of the system.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"images/banners/Indonesias%20Automotive%20Industry%204.0%20Symposium%20Infor-.JPG\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Indonesia’s Automotive Industry 4.0 Symposium\" title=\"Indonesia’s Automotive Industry 4.0 Symposium Infor\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lastly, Mr. Noel Sebastian as Senior Principal Partner manager for Infor presents about Infor ERP LN product lifecycle policy. The product life cycle is the three phases of maintenance for Infor software and provides visibility into what is expected of Infor Support and Infor Maintenance at each stage in the product life cycle. During each stage the components available are different. Maintaining the product is important as it provides a predictable policy that governs applications support and maintenance to enable better planning and control of your Infor software upgrade strategy. The event ends with the door prize draw and photo session.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">PT BSI has aspirations as the host of Automotive Industry event is to educate automotive industry practitioners to be aware of the trend change, about global challenges and also regarding how to execute preventive actions in responding to the global challenges.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">For more information about the solution please contact our phone at +6221 304 90008 or <a href=\"https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=628111221789&amp;text=Hallo%20PT%20Realta...\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Whatsapp\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WhatsApp +628111221789</a> (Chat Only) or our email at ptbsi@ptbsi.co.id<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 87, '2020-02-28 08:13:46', 862, '', '2021-03-02 04:07:06', 863, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2020-02-28 08:13:46', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"images\\/banners\\/Indonesias Automotive Industry 4.0 Symposium Header.jpg\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vo